## Remarks  
 <span data-ttu-id="a82cb-102"><xref:System.Runtime.Caching.MemoryCache> 类是抽象 <xref:System.Runtime.Caching.ObjectCache> 类的具体实现。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a82cb-102">The <xref:System.Runtime.Caching.MemoryCache> class is a concrete implementation of the abstract <xref:System.Runtime.Caching.ObjectCache> class.</span></span>  
  
> [!NOTE]
>  <span data-ttu-id="a82cb-103"><xref:System.Runtime.Caching.MemoryCache>类是类似于 ASP.NET<xref:System.Web.Caching.Cache>类。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a82cb-103">The <xref:System.Runtime.Caching.MemoryCache> class is similar to the ASP.NET <xref:System.Web.Caching.Cache> class.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="a82cb-104"><xref:System.Runtime.Caching.MemoryCache>类具有许多属性和方法用于访问缓存，如果您用过 ASP.NET 将为你所熟悉<xref:System.Web.Caching.Cache>类。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a82cb-104">The <xref:System.Runtime.Caching.MemoryCache> class has many properties and methods for accessing the cache that will be familiar to you if you have used the ASP.NET <xref:System.Web.Caching.Cache> class.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="a82cb-105">之间的主要区别<xref:System.Web.Caching.Cache>并<xref:System.Runtime.Caching.MemoryCache>类是<xref:System.Runtime.Caching.MemoryCache>类已更改，以使其可由[!INCLUDE[dnprdnshort](~/includes/dnprdnshort-md.md)]不是 ASP.NET 应用程序的应用程序。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a82cb-105">The main differences between the <xref:System.Web.Caching.Cache> and <xref:System.Runtime.Caching.MemoryCache> classes are that the <xref:System.Runtime.Caching.MemoryCache> class has been changed to make it usable by [!INCLUDE[dnprdnshort](~/includes/dnprdnshort-md.md)] applications that are not ASP.NET applications.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="a82cb-106">例如，<xref:System.Runtime.Caching.MemoryCache>类并不依赖于`System.Web`程序集。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a82cb-106">For example, the <xref:System.Runtime.Caching.MemoryCache> class has no dependencies on the `System.Web` assembly.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="a82cb-107">另一个区别是您可以创建多个实例<xref:System.Runtime.Caching.MemoryCache>类以使用在同一应用程序和相同<xref:System.AppDomain>实例。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a82cb-107">Another difference is that you can create multiple instances of the <xref:System.Runtime.Caching.MemoryCache> class for use in the same application and in the same <xref:System.AppDomain> instance.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="a82cb-108"><xref:System.Runtime.Caching.MemoryCache>类不允许`null`为缓存中的值。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a82cb-108">The <xref:System.Runtime.Caching.MemoryCache> class does not allow `null` as a value in the cache.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="a82cb-109">若要添加或更改的值与某个缓存项的任何尝试`null`将失败。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a82cb-109">Any attempt to add or change a cache entry with a value of `null` will fail.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="a82cb-110"><xref:System.Runtime.Caching.MemoryCache>类型不实现*缓存区域*。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a82cb-110">The <xref:System.Runtime.Caching.MemoryCache> type does not implement *cache regions*.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="a82cb-111">因此，当调用<xref:System.Runtime.Caching.MemoryCache>实现包含区域，参数的基方法的方法不传递参数的值。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a82cb-111">Therefore, when you call <xref:System.Runtime.Caching.MemoryCache> methods that implement base methods that contain a parameter for regions, do not pass a value for the parameter.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="a82cb-112">使用区域参数的所有方法提供一个默认`null`值。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a82cb-112">The methods that use the region parameter all supply a default `null` value.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="a82cb-113">例如，<xref:System.Runtime.Caching.MemoryCache.AddOrGetExisting%2A?displayProperty=nameWithType>方法重载已`regionName`参数，其默认值是`null`。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a82cb-113">For example, the <xref:System.Runtime.Caching.MemoryCache.AddOrGetExisting%2A?displayProperty=nameWithType> method overload has a `regionName` parameter whose default value is `null`.</span></span>  
  
   
  
## Examples  
 <span data-ttu-id="a82cb-114">下面的示例声明默认内存缓存实例的引用。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a82cb-114">The following example declares a reference to the default memory cache instance.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="a82cb-115">缓存项使用<xref:System.Runtime.Caching.CacheItemPolicy>对象提供的缓存项的逐出和过期详细信息。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a82cb-115">The cache entry uses a <xref:System.Runtime.Caching.CacheItemPolicy> object to provide eviction and expiration details for the cache entry.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="a82cb-116">它还使用<xref:System.Runtime.Caching.ChangeMonitor>要监视文件系统上的源数据 （即文件） 的状态对象。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a82cb-116">It also uses a <xref:System.Runtime.Caching.ChangeMonitor> object to monitor the state of the source data (which is a file) on the file system.</span></span>  
  
```vb  
Private Sub btnGet_Click(ByVal sender As Object, ByVal e As EventArgs)   
    Dim cache As ObjectCache = MemoryCache.[Default]   
    Dim fileContents As String = TryCast(cache("filecontents"), String)   
  
    If fileContents Is Nothing Then   
        Dim policy As New CacheItemPolicy()   
        Dim filePaths As New List(Of String)()   
        filePaths.Add("c:\cache\example.txt")   
  
        policy.ChangeMonitors.Add(New HostFileChangeMonitor(filePaths))   
  
        ' Fetch the file contents.  
        fileContents = File.ReadAllText("c:\cache\example.txt")   
  
        cache.[Set]("filecontents", fileContents, policy)   
    End If   
  
    Label1.Text = fileContents  
End Sub  
```  
  
```csharp  
private void btnGet_Click(object sender, EventArgs e)  
{  
    ObjectCache cache = MemoryCache.Default;  
    string fileContents = cache["filecontents"] as string;  
  
    if (fileContents == null)  
    {  
        CacheItemPolicy policy = new CacheItemPolicy();  
  
        List<string> filePaths = new List<string>();  
        filePaths.Add("c:\\cache\\example.txt");  
  
        policy.ChangeMonitors.Add(new   
        HostFileChangeMonitor(filePaths));  
  
        // Fetch the file contents.  
        fileContents =   
            File.ReadAllText("c:\\cache\\example.txt");  
  
        cache.Set("filecontents", fileContents, policy);  
    }  
  
    Label1.Text = fileContents;  
}  
```
